### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{TEST_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{TEST_PASSWORD}}"
}

### Set token variable from login response
@token = {{login.token}}

### ===========================================
### POST SECTIONS ENDPOINTS (CREATE)
### ===========================================

### Create Section
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/sections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "division": "01",
  "section_code": "01",
  "section_name": "Development Section",
  "remarks": "Software development and engineering team",
  "status": "Active"
}
